{
  "stem": "19242.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did go in the mikveh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I never hear that about-- so they said, maybe there were some, but not too many women need to go to the mikveh.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe you're right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know my mother didn't go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think he had that little mustache, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No payos.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, didn't-- when he were in the business, he didn't wear no hat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On Shabbos when we go-- when we eat a meal, he wear a yarmulke and make a bracha and then we seated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Friday night, the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my-- my-- my zayde did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did wear a kapota.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was more-- he was-- he was more-- because the business-- it was my zayde's business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had two sons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one-- the other son was in Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the two-- the business left by him for my father and Tzike.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he got kind of older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said he don't want to-- He used to come still there, but he was not too active.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happened then, yeah, then the brothers had kind of an argument.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they split up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had to pay him out so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had-- it's in the same business but maybe-- and let's see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe about 10 businesses, I think he opened up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were-- he was successful too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What kind of business?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hardware business.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had the hardware business, and then we had the factory that was making farm machinery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after that they made the machine shop near the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think it was a half a block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was then working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had to machine it and then assemble it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
